@startuml
title UC06 - Match Lifecycle State
[*] --> Scheduled : create
Scheduled --> Live : match time reached (lock predictions)
Scheduled --> Cancelled : Admin cancels
Live --> Finished : Admin enters official result + criterion results
Finished --> Scored : system scores predictions (+1/correct)
Scored --> PaidOut : gold pool split among winners (>=1 score)
PaidOut --> Notified : MATCH_WON / MATCH_LOST sent
Live --> Cancelled : match cancelled
Cancelled --> VoidedNotified : void results + MATCH_CANCELLED sent
Scheduled --> [*] : soft delete if no related data
Notified --> [*]
VoidedNotified --> [*]
note right of PaidOut
  pool = entry_gold * participants;
  gold_won = pool / winners (2 decimals);
  < 2 participants -> không tính leaderboard.
end note
@enduml
